# SauceDemo Playwright Tests

This repository contains automated tests for the SauceDemo website using Playwright. The tests include user login and adding an item to the cart.

## Prerequisites

- Node.js (v12 or higher)
- npm (v6 or higher) or yarn

## Setup

1. Clone the repository:

    ```sh
    git clone https://github.com/buhgalterok83/js_test_hw.git
    cd saucedemo-playwright-tests
    ```

2. Install the dependencies:

    ```sh
    npm install
    ```

    or

    ```sh
    yarn install
    ```

## Running Tests

To execute the tests, use the following command:

```sh
npx playwright test
